### Time Investment

Magical crafting cannot be rushed:

**Minor Items:** Days of work (potions, scrolls, +1 weapons)
**Moderate Items:** Weeks of work (wands, +2 weapons, specialized armor)
**Major Items:** Months of work (artifacts, legendary weapons, reality-altering items)

This time must be focused—you can adventure between crafting sessions, but each session requires several hours of uninterrupted work. Most crafters create minor items between adventures, commissioning moderate items during downtime, and pursuing major items as long-term campaign goals.

